      <section eId="sec_CCRP-831">
        <num>CCRP 831</num>
        <heading>PRESENCE OF DEFENDENT</heading>
        <subsection eId="CCRP-831__subsec_A">
          <num>A.</num>
          <content>
            <p>Except as may be provided by local rules of court in accordance with Articles
522, 551, and 562, a defendant charged with a felony shall be present at all of the following:</p>
          </content>
          <paragraph eId="CCRP-831__subsec_A__subsec_1">
            <num>(1)</num>
            <content>
              <p>At arraignment.</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph eId="CCRP-831__subsec_A__subsec_2">
            <num>(2)</num>
            <content>
              <p>When a plea of guilty, not guilty, or not guilty and not guilty by reason of insanity
is made.</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph eId="CCRP-831__subsec_A__subsec_3">
            <num>(3)</num>
            <content>
              <p>At the calling, examination, challenging, impaneling, and swearing of the jury,
and at any subsequent proceedings for the discharge of the jury or of a juror.</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph eId="CCRP-831__subsec_A__subsec_4">
            <num>(4)</num>
            <content>
              <p>At all times during the trial when the court is determining and ruling on the
admissibility of evidence.</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph eId="CCRP-831__subsec_A__subsec_5">
            <num>(5)</num>
            <content>
              <p>In trials by jury, at all proceedings when the jury is present, and in trials without
a jury, at all times when evidence is being adduced.</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph eId="CCRP-831__subsec_A__subsec_6">
            <num>(6)</num>
            <content>
              <p>At the rendition of the verdict or judgment, unless he voluntarily absents himself.</p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CCRP-831__subsec_B">
          <num>B.</num>
          <content>
            <p>Repealed by</p>
          </content>
